Collard Greens - or kale / mustard greens
Ham Hock (smoked slimjim)
1 cup Sugar
1/2 cup salt
3 tbsp crushed red pepper

Boil hocks until start to fall apart. Transfer hocks to boiling water. Shiny-side in, fold leaves and remove stems. Bring brine water to a boil and reduce to simmer. Simmer covered for 45 minutes.
